{"tid":680490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好似無人post] 一到大熱天時睇蘋果真係一大樂事","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T08:32:22.000Z","uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d211c3c879b942c75e480f784ca537cbe40dfc20","tid":680490,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/162843_aa622f91734a909ce9369e2487669fc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F162843_aa622f91734a909ce9369e2487669fc3.png&h=dd27fae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台昨在市區錄得最高34.7&deg;C，是連續第10日酷熱，再刷新歷來5月最長酷熱紀錄。陽光充沛，加上濕度不低，令體感溫度比天文台公佈的氣溫更高；民間氣象組織「地下天文台」利用官方公佈的氣溫和濕度數據，計算「酷熱指數」 <a href=\"http://www.weather.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weather.org.hk&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2Fi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f268e3a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.weather.org.hk</a> ，至今日上午近12時，部份市區體感溫度超過逾40&deg;C，戶外活動可能會熱衰竭，而坪洲的體感溫度一度更高達44.5&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，天文台亦有公佈類似體感氣溫的「暑熱指數」，不過其位於市區的京士柏氣象站，昨午度出的指數不超過31&deg;C，較地下天文台計算該站的「酷熱指數」（逾38&deg;C）低逾7度。至於設於郊區、上水雙魚河的氣象站，昨午度出的「暑熱指數」亦不超過30&deg;C，遠低於地下天文台計算的上水「酷熱指數」（逾41&deg;C）多達11度。<br />\n<br />\n天文台科學主任黎宏駿向《蘋果》解釋，天文台公佈的「暑熱指數」，是由氣象站另設的獨立儀器，測量濕球、黑球和乾球溫度後，經方程式計算出來（ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2sbuG6l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sbuG6l&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2Fi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=dcfbefad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2sbuG6l</a> ），而有關方程式是由同事研究所得。至於地下天文台計算的「酷熱指數」，相信是利用天文台公佈的各區氣溫和濕度數據，再套用美國氣象局的方程式計算出來，故兩者有分別。<br />\n<br />\n至今日上午10時許，京士柏和雙魚河的「暑熱指數」分別為30.6及29.5。當天文台公佈的「暑熱指數」高於30&deg;C，市民要做好防暑措施；天文台亦會參考「暑熱指數」，決定是否發出酷熱警告。黎宏駿表示，現時天文台只於京士柏和雙魚河量度「暑熱指數」，至於日後會否在更多氣象站增設儀器測量，則要視乎該區環境是否適合安裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180527&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58242183 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180527%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58242183%20&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2Fi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7de7e54f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180527%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58242183%20&h=0de061a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180527&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58242183 </a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178327e395bfa4227bb03383130cb58d41366ead","tid":680490,"uid":145975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc2bf0771db92631c8521e2816c8fa1d3b5f390","tid":680490,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"其實係沙灘拎大機影相，係外國同香港分別出現咩情境💁🏻&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"7b0ef4b6831b9e8df40b4c8b9a1ad1060219c56a","tid":680490,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"睇唔到樣 你老母都正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cbba21f50aeb86bed3a9cb19969d5582da68c2","tid":680490,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0ef4b6831b9e8df40b4c8b9a1ad1060219c56a","tid":680490,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"睇唔到樣 你老母都正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"又啱喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似snapchat狗filter 咁，個個都變女神"},{"pid":"02dfe301a9769988ff9785b6c47a9f0137ace030","tid":680490,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dc2bf0771db92631c8521e2816c8fa1d3b5f390","tid":680490,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"其實係沙灘拎大機影相，係外國同香港分別出現咩情境💁🏻&zwj;♀️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"